{"tid":835066,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【憑咩？】99.9%虛構科幻打J片《紅海行動》代表香港提名角逐奧斯卡最佳外語片","createTime":"2018-09-24T14:53:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T01:11:44.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"37187be21be2f01a05dff76da3dba35e6f447905","tid":835066,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T14:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180924/large/1537787262_6561.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180924%2Flarge%2F1537787262_6561.jpg&h=04d4e5a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180924/58719406\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180924%2F58719406&d=p7V8kcw7At%2BzUZ8v1VxoIYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=7d56e0c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180924%2F58719406&h=d010c07f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180924/58719406</a><br />\n<br />\n一部代表香港嘅電影，起碼演員係香港人、幕後係香港人、出品公司都係香港公司。但係近年唔少香港電影，都被大陸人、大陸嘅元素入侵，咁仲算唔算係香港電影呢？<br />\n<br />\n今日呢個「香港電影製片家協會」公佈咗，以電影《紅海行動》代表香港，提名角逐「第91屆奧斯卡」嘅「最佳外語片」。呢部《紅海行動》憑咩呢？除咗導演林超賢係香港人之外，班演員張譯、海清、黃景瑜、杜江，唔識唔出奇，因為佢哋係大陸演員，而且套戲嘅故仔係講解放軍海軍陸戰隊，關香港咩事呢？<br />\n<br />\n至於呢部《紅海行動》，之前因為明星逃稅事件，引發官方同軍方嘅權鬥角力，有傳官方曾經下達「禁軍令」，限制軍方背景嘅公司及電影，當時呢部宣揚民族主義嘅《紅海行動》曾遭官方內部狠批。<br />\n<br />\n睇番「香港電影製片家協會」嘅公佈，佢哋話董事局成員，由2017年10月至2018年9月份期間上映之所有香港電影中挑選，從最後入圍嘅七部電影包括《奇門遁甲》、《紅海行動》、《捉妖記2》、《黃金兄弟》、《棟篤特工》、《藍天白雲》同《中英街1號》中，選出《紅海行動》代表香港，無錯係代表香港去參加角逐奧斯卡「最佳外語片」。<br />\n<br />\n香港影業協會主席洪祖星今日接受本報電話訪問，講解入圍美國奧斯卡金像獎嘅資格，佢話：「《紅海行動》嘅攝影、劇本、導演同埋製片人都係香港人，最緊要出品公司係香港資金，所以係合符資格。洪祖星話奧斯卡以投資公司同製片人嘅國籍做依歸，同金像獎嘅入圍資格好唔同，佢話：「金像獎要主要演員有香港人，奧斯卡主要係睇邊個畀錢同producer。」洪祖星透露係由15名奧斯卡委員，一人一票選出代表香港嘅電影，喺7部入圍電影，《紅》片得票都幾一面倒。"},{"pid":"11db99d6642bae484e4b7a345d0207d248cf9353","tid":835066,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T14:53:47.000Z","msg":"收錢收到fat fat<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"171381272a634e9da6b041960eefbf3bec3a9a48","tid":835066,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11db99d6642bae484e4b7a345d0207d248cf9353","tid":835066,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T14:53:47.000Z","msg":"收錢收到fat fat<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T15:15:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb128fb49ece70912535083defe496b09842c669","tid":835066,"uid":99205,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T15:20:17.000Z","msg":"又借香港個名用<br />\n真係好洗好用"},{"pid":"168bf76458c514736ed7c4e040f43d4602c5c3f7","tid":835066,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T18:04:09.000Z","msg":"手撕日本仔啲fd？"},{"pid":"e1cdcb3ca17421972e0ccd46ed2791cf4f0f05f9","tid":835066,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb128fb49ece70912535083defe496b09842c669","tid":835066,"uid":99205,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T15:20:17.000Z","msg":"又借香港個名用<br />\n真係好洗好用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T18:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d912e84aee9a68980f6d786b8b8e35216e41c4ba","tid":835066,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T22:48:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848180684191969ca98852c9945a06872f1fed68","tid":835066,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T01:11:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://去Oscar.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%8E%BBOscar.org&d=p7V8kcw7At%2BzUZ8v1VxoIYM9Luu